\begin_layout Standard
This latter period had several dimensions.
 Emphasizing the social relations of landed property and its multiple forms
 in contemporary capitalism, some scholars rejected the possibility of a
 general theory of rent and instead emphasized 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

ideographic
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 empirical research on specific situations; opposing this, others emphasized
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

